snippet.title: Mega Man X Online: Deathmatch V1.0 Release Trailer!
snippet.description:
After months of hard work, the MMX Online Deathmatch fan project is now officially released and out of beta! Now with online multiplayer! Download it here from the game's main website:
https://gamemaker19.github.io/MMXOnlineDesktop/
Join the Discord server here for discussion, help, and finding players online! https://discord.gg/kP9XtVU

All credit goes to Capcom for Mega Man franchise and resources used. Not affiliated with Capcom in any way.
